# Vault

[Vault](https://www.vaultproject.io/) is used to handle all secrets within the Connect infrastructure.

Configuration of Vault is handled in the Connect Deployment [repo](https://github.com/cabinetoffice/national-leadership-centre-deployment/tree/master/vault).

Information on how to connect with Vault can be found in the [readme](https://github.com/cabinetoffice/national-leadership-centre-deployment/tree/master/vault).